Detail view: user-visible content + screenshot (signed URL) + the full diagnostics blob
rendered as collapsible sections. Code ownership block shows file:line as a clickable
reference and the breadcrumb. Include a "copy dev bundle" button (reuse the copy-dev-info
affordance already in TopbarAlerts).

Triage actions: change status/severity, assign, add comment (Phase 6). Every action writes to
the hash-chained audit log.

Pin to code state: show commit_sha/ref/build_id prominently so a dev knows the exact code the
