PATCH /api/support/reports/[id] — admin only. Status/severity/assignee; audit-logged.

DB helper: src/lib/database/support.js (matches the <domain>.js convention) — all Supabase
queries live here, never in pages/components. Functions: createSupportReport, listSupportReports,
