changed, report deleted/purged. entityType: 'support_report'.

Permissions matrix:

Action	Who
Open "?" popup / submit a report	Any authenticated user
See own report's user-visible status	Reporter (optional, Phase 6)
View report list / diagnostics bundle	DEV_FULL_ACCESS_ROLES (admin/owner/admin manager)
Triage (status/severity/assign/comment)	Admin/owner
