12. Storage strategy
Bucket: new private support-reports bucket (do not reuse job-files/vhc-customer-media
— keeps retention/ACL separate). Path: support-reports/{reportId}/screenshot.{ext}.

Create via the ensureBucket helper pattern (storageService.js), public: false.

Upload server-side with supabaseService after the row exists (so path includes the report id);
